<HL>
   Canada Brokers
   Share the Woes
   Of Wall Street
   ----
   By Suzanne McGee
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
06/25/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE C1
</SO>
